      "title": "Prompts 👇",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Prompts are optional and usually unnecessary.  \nWe are generating a small number of frames, and VACE operates more from the motion cues in the context frames than from the prompt.  \nAnd of course the negative prompt is ineffective at CFG=1 without NAG."
