      "title": "👆 VACE Parameters",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "**The defaults, `context_frames=8` and `replace_frames=8` usually work well for most 16 fps videos.**\n> - **context_frames**: The number of reference frames from each side of the transition.\n> - **replace_frames**: The number of frames from each input clip that will be replaced by new frames generated by VACE. `replace_frames`=8 means 16 frames will be generated at the transition.\n> - **new_frames**: the number of brand new frames to generate at the transition in addition to `replace_frames`, extending the  joined clip.\n\nThis workflow will generate `(context_frames * 2) + (replace_frames * 2) + new_frames` frames at the transition. The first and last `context_frames` mirror existing frames from the input videos."
      ],
      "color": "#233",
      "bgcolor": "#355"
    },
